cols2Text {SparkBeyond}R Documentation

cols2Text

Description

Convert all data columns into a serializable text/primitive representation. Cells that contain lists will be converted to [ , , ] representation. All strings will quoted.

Usage

cols2Text(data)

Arguments

data:

dataframe / data.table to convert to primitive represenation.

Value

a vector containing all input information in text/primitive representation

Examples

grouped = groupBy(getData("titanic_train"), by =list("pclass","sex"))
textGrouped = cols2Text(grouped)
typeOfCols(textGrouped)
